07:44.890 --> 07:47.890
[Bed clunks up the stairs]

08:21.800 --> 08:23.730
[Crunching chips]

08:34.710 --> 08:37.980
[Tapping keyboard]

08:41.350 --> 08:43.320
[Printing]

09:15.420 --> 09:20.390
Man: You should do what that guy
in the mid South did.

09:20.890 --> 09:22.220
- Did he go to law school?

09:22.220 --> 09:23.520
'Cause that's what
I shoulda done.

09:23.530 --> 09:24.590
- No.

09:25.190 --> 09:28.460
No, he put an ad...

09:28.930 --> 09:31.230
or like a notice online.

09:32.430 --> 09:35.040
And was calling for
actors for his slasher film.

09:36.040 --> 09:38.640
So this amateur actor guy
answers the call.

09:38.640 --> 09:42.740
And the dude says, come on over.

09:42.880 --> 09:44.340
We're shooting in my basement.

09:44.910 --> 09:47.280
And this poor amateur dude
has never acted before.

09:47.650 --> 09:49.320
So, he doesn't
think that's weird.

09:49.550 --> 09:50.620
So, he goes on over.

09:50.620 --> 09:52.990
And of course, the director
looks normal.

09:53.320 --> 09:55.190
Oh, and before that,
the director -

09:55.190 --> 10:02.200
He sends the actor guy some
footage, or stuff to look at.

10:02.200 --> 10:03.730
And it looks legit.

10:03.730 --> 10:05.230
So, he goes on over.

10:05.230 --> 10:07.600
And of course, the director is
completely off his tits.

10:07.600 --> 10:10.040
Psycho.

10:10.040 --> 10:12.470
And the guy, the actor guy,
he doesn't know what hit him

10:12.470 --> 10:13.970
Until he's tied to a chair.

10:13.980 --> 10:15.710
And the director
is slicing him up.

10:17.580 --> 10:18.780
Musta looked real, though.

10:18.780 --> 10:21.820
Because it was real.

10:28.920 --> 10:31.060
- I don't like actors.

10:32.360 --> 10:33.760
Vile human beings.

10:35.730 --> 10:36.960
Selfish.

10:39.100 --> 10:40.770
What happened to the guy?

10:40.770 --> 10:42.770
- Oh man. The police found
him almost immediately.

10:42.770 --> 10:44.270
I'm pretty sure they killed him.

10:45.610 --> 10:46.740
- Good advice.

10:48.380 --> 10:50.010
- Well, pin it on somebody else.

10:50.610 --> 10:52.050
I dunno. Where's your idea?

10:53.350 --> 10:54.280
[Phone buzzes]

10:58.590 --> 11:00.990
It's been every five
minutes for days now.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.160
I'm dead.

11:07.830 --> 11:09.860
- So what's wrong with
my idea then?

11:10.030 --> 11:11.770
- What's wrong with your idea?

11:11.770 --> 11:13.830
- Oh, does it go
against your ethical code?

11:16.170 --> 11:18.270
It goes against my ethical code.

11:18.510 --> 11:19.570
- I've seen your movies, man.

11:21.040 --> 11:22.480
You don't have an ethical code.

11:23.310 --> 11:25.530
Plus, with my idea,

11:25.530 --> 11:27.750
you don't have to waste money
on make-up and effects.

11:37.590 --> 11:38.560
- What about...

11:41.800 --> 11:44.300
What about crew, cameras,
and all that?

11:45.100 --> 11:47.630
- Jesus Patrick, I gotta come up
with all the answers for you?

11:47.640 --> 11:48.670
Goddamn.

11:52.510 --> 11:56.040
I fucking hate movies.

11:56.950 --> 11:59.380
