19:00.470 --> 19:01.600
Hello?

19:03.300 --> 19:04.470
Hello?

19:18.990 --> 19:19.890
Hello?

19:27.130 --> 19:28.830
Is anyone here?

19:46.480 --> 19:47.810
Gross.

20:21.680 --> 20:23.620
Well, this must be
the right spot.

21:26.080 --> 21:27.180
- Who are you?

21:27.650 --> 21:28.550
[Gasps]

21:28.980 --> 21:31.720
Oh, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

21:31.720 --> 21:32.950
Did I just jump scare you?

21:32.950 --> 21:34.890
Yes!

21:35.460 --> 21:36.620
That is the worst.

21:36.620 --> 21:38.190
You must hate me now, don't you?

21:38.490 --> 21:40.190
I'm... That's so cheap.

21:40.190 --> 21:41.890
I shoulda made more noise
coming up the stairs.

21:41.900 --> 21:44.860
No, um... I'm fine.

21:45.300 --> 21:47.070
Are you sure you're
not gonna die?

21:47.440 --> 21:50.670
- No. I'll survive.

21:51.870 --> 21:53.570
And do you remember your name?

21:54.480 --> 21:56.580
Yes. It's...

21:57.980 --> 21:59.150
It's Grace.

21:59.150 --> 22:03.520
I don't know if that's true or
not, because I just met you.

22:03.520 --> 22:05.380
But I'll take your word for it.

22:06.220 --> 22:07.190
I promise.

22:07.590 --> 22:08.520
Great.

22:08.760 --> 22:10.060
I'm Foster.

22:10.060 --> 22:11.290
I'm acting in this movie.

22:11.290 --> 22:13.660
And I'm guessing you are too.

22:14.200 --> 22:15.700
Yeah, I am.

22:15.700 --> 22:17.100
I'm an actress.

22:18.130 --> 22:19.700
Then you'll fit right in.

22:19.870 --> 22:22.400
Come on. I'll take you to
meet everyone else.

22:23.070 --> 22:24.340
Okay?
- Okay.

22:26.810 --> 22:29.440
